<item>
            <title>[LU-12694] make &quot;lfs quota&quot; display correct group quota information</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12694</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lfs quota (without -g option) doesn&apos;t show correct group quota information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
# lfs quota /lustre/
Disk quotas &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; usr root (uid 0):
     Filesystem  kbytes   quota   limit   grace   files   quota   limit   grace
       /lustre/   13208       0       0       -    1096       0       0       -
Disk quotas &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; grp root (gid 0):
     Filesystem  kbytes   quota   limit   grace   files   quota   limit   grace
       /lustre/       0       0       0       -       0       0       0       -

* kbytes(0 is dispolayed) should be 13208

# lfs quota -g root /lustre/
Disk quotas &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; grp root (gid 0):
     Filesystem  kbytes   quota   limit   grace   files   quota   limit   grace
       /lustre/   13208       0       0       -    1096       0       0       -
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is because, on the server side GETQUOTA is not executed when oqctl-&amp;gt;qc_dqblk.dqb_curspace not 0. So, qctl.qc_dqblk need to be cleared to display correct.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; quotactl_ioctl(struct ll_sb_info *sbi, struct if_quotactl *qctl)
{
&amp;lt;snip&amp;gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (cmd == Q_GETQUOTA &amp;amp;&amp;amp;
                    !(oqctl-&amp;gt;qc_dqblk.dqb_valid &amp;amp; QIF_SPACE) &amp;amp;&amp;amp;
                    !oqctl-&amp;gt;qc_dqblk.dqb_curspace) {
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
